      <h1>Participation Guide</h1>
      <p>
        This User Guide aims to help you gain the maximum 
        <a href="benefits.html">benefit from participating</a> in your
        Online Groups.
      </p>
      <p>

        Often you want to 
        <a href="keep-track.html">keep track of conversations</a> in online 
        groups, without reading every post. 
        At other times, you wish to 
        <a href="follow_closely.html">follow a conversation closely</a>, or to
        <a href="contribute.html">contribute to a conversation</a>. 
        This guide explains different ways to do these things.
      </p>
